# Input

```html
<div
  id="hello"
  class="world really-long-class-name another-really-long-class-name"
  style="color: red"
  data-foo="bar"
  data-bar="foo"
>
  hello world
</div>

```


# Options

```json
{
  "$schema": "../../../../../../../../packages/@biomejs/biome/configuration_schema.json",
  "formatter": {
    "bracketSameLine": true
  }
}
```

# Formatted

```html
<div
	id="hello"
	class="world really-long-class-name another-really-long-class-name"
	style="color: red"
	data-foo="bar"
	data-bar="foo">
	hello world
</div>

```
